\subsection{Response format}{

After a successful edit, the response includes updated hashline references
for the edited regions (plus 1 line of surrounding context). When edits
change the total line count, the response includes shift hints that tell
the model how to adjust any cached line numbers without re-reading the
entire file (e.g. "update line numbers by +2").
